{"tid":2251431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[防暴毆打示威者] 芝加哥七人案：驚世審判  The Trial of the Chicago 7","createTime":"2020-10-20T20:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T06:50:00.000Z","uid":205105,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"43d37c8984615c7dee8a00e7858d6e6b25346095","tid":2251431,"uid":205105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T20:46:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FVb6EdKDBfU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFVb6EdKDBfU&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=4685e394\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FVb6EdKDBfU</a><br />\n先姑勿論套戲用左咩大CAST，喺而家風頭火勢，因為NETFLIX夠獨立先可以繼續支持呢類敏感題材。而家睇呢類戲真係感觸良多<br />\n從歷史中學習，或者今日可以有人控制法庭將提出反對意見嘅人送入監獄，但只要大眾有共同意志，我地都可以有香港嘅Tom Hayden，改革香港嘅民主進程<br />\n就算以司法制度自豪嘅美國都曾經有法官未審先判嘅歷史，要知道進步好多時都唔係一步登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但願我地可以行得再快少少<br />\n<br />\n今日係13個月，雖然日撚日睇住班官喺度鳩噏，雖然政府DQ左我地張選票，但係我地仲有鈔票，用之前三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啤酒要飲嘉士伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA court ought not be affected by the weather of the day, but will be the climate of the era. <br />\n- Paul A. Freund"},{"pid":"0396c8cad7176ef076960f61c7d8c386276a2cf7","tid":2251431,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T20:52:59.000Z","msg":"左膠又攞上一代來打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73354cd157ede3f428d0ad99ea01c3ea34b39bbf","tid":2251431,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:11:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9575d11bb0f017e7ee1